{
    "ai-snp2.7:0.1_0": "Sutta Nipāta 2.7",
    "ai-snp2.7:0.2_0": "Brāhmaṇadhammikasutta",
    "ai-snp2.7:1.1_0": "So I have heard.",
    "ai-snp2.7:1.2_0": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery.",
    "ai-snp2.7:1.3_0": "Then several well-to-do brahmins who are old, elderly and senior, who were advanced in years and had reached the final stage of life.",
    "ai-snp2.7:1.3_1": "they exchanged pleasantries with him,",
    "ai-snp2.7:1.4_0": "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, they sat down to one side,",
    "ai-snp2.7:1.5_0": "The Buddha said,",
    "ai-snp2.7:1.6_0": "“Master Gotama, are the brahmins a teacher’s tradition?”",
    "ai-snp2.7:1.7_0": "“These days brahmins aren’t ancient, brahmins.”",
    "ai-snp2.7:1.8_0": "“Good Gotama, please teach us so very Dhamma.”",
    "ai-snp2.7:1.9_0": "“Well then, brahmins, listen and pay close attention, I will speak.”",
    "ai-snp2.7:1.10_0": "“Yes sir,” those well-to-do brahmins replied.",
    "ai-snp2.7:1.11_0": "The Buddha said to him:",
    "ai-snp2.7:2.1_0": "“Among the past,",
    "ai-snp2.7:2.2_0": "by their self-mortification,",
    "ai-snp2.7:2.3_0": "having given up the five sensual titillations,",
    "ai-snp2.7:2.4_0": "made a mistake.",
    "ai-snp2.7:3.1_0": "ascended by the brahmins",
    "ai-snp2.7:3.2_0": "for excitement,",
    "ai-snp2.7:3.3_0": "all the consummations and the gods,",
    "ai-snp2.7:3.4_0": "they seek the keepers of Brahmā.",
    "ai-snp2.7:4.1_0": "Whatever fame",
    "ai-snp2.7:4.2_0": "gates to the recipient and nursen:",
    "ai-snp2.7:4.3_0": "They feed on faith,",
    "ai-snp2.7:4.4_0": "while he was still here.",
    "ai-snp2.7:5.1_0": "Overcome by different words,",
    "ai-snp2.7:5.2_0": "like moths and cries;",
    "ai-snp2.7:5.3_0": "Pessavaṇas, countries,",
    "ai-snp2.7:5.4_0": "they revere the brahmins.",
    "ai-snp2.7:6.1_0": "Other brahmins",
    "ai-snp2.7:6.2_0": "in a principled manner,",
    "ai-snp2.7:6.3_0": "No-one always goes on,",
    "ai-snp2.7:6.4_0": "they’ve gone to all the family.",
    "ai-snp2.7:7.1_0": "By the eight years old",
    "ai-snp2.7:7.2_0": "said to the spiritual life,",
    "ai-snp2.7:7.3_0": "with knowledge and conduct,",
    "ai-snp2.7:7.4_0": "as well as brahmins.",
    "ai-snp2.7:8.1_0": "I don’t believe in the brahmin,",
    "ai-snp2.7:8.2_0": "nor did they admit,",
    "ai-snp2.7:8.3_0": "are always waiting for a place",
    "ai-snp2.7:8.4_0": "but then they got together.",
    "ai-snp2.7:9.1_0": "except on an appropriate occasion,",
    "ai-snp2.7:9.2_0": "Paying alone.",
    "ai-snp2.7:9.3_0": "Having sexual intercourse,",
    "ai-snp2.7:9.4_0": "yet they still go to the brahmins.",
    "ai-snp2.7:10.1_0": "O spiritual path,",
    "ai-snp2.7:10.2_0": "trampled, the Tapussa,",
    "ai-snp2.7:10.3_0": "they’re ignorant and incompetent,",
    "ai-snp2.7:10.4_0": "and even the maids gave them.",
    "ai-snp2.7:11.1_0": "Anyone who gave you",
    "ai-snp2.7:11.2_0": "Brahmā realm, and strength,",
    "ai-snp2.7:11.3_0": "Even if they have sexual intercourse,",
    "ai-snp2.7:11.4_0": "Supassa for him.",
    "ai-snp2.7:12.1_0": "and transformed themselves,",
    "ai-snp2.7:12.2_0": "were present to him like this,",
    "ai-snp2.7:12.3_0": "O spiritual path,",
    "ai-snp2.7:12.4_0": "and even the maids gave them.",
    "ai-snp2.7:13.1_0": "food, drink, clothes, and bedding;",
    "ai-snp2.7:13.2_0": "And he asked for ghee;",
    "ai-snp2.7:13.3_0": "Skilled in principle,",
    "ai-snp2.7:13.4_0": "they went to the sacrifice.",
    "ai-snp2.7:14.1_0": "Bath in sacrifice,",
    "ai-snp2.7:14.2_0": "they borrowed the cows,",
    "ai-snp2.7:14.3_0": "Mother, father, and brother",
    "ai-snp2.7:14.4_0": "would do you more good",
    "ai-snp2.7:14.5_0": "“The cattle are ultimate friends,",
    "ai-snp2.7:14.6_0": "among the things that we’re born.",
    "ai-snp2.7:15.1_0": "From whence wrong,",
    "ai-snp2.7:15.2_0": "sometimes giving and happiness,",
    "ai-snp2.7:15.3_0": "Knowing the reason for this,",
    "ai-snp2.7:15.4_0": "And they didn’t kill the cows.",
    "ai-snp2.7:16.1_0": "Great Hell is delicate and small,",
    "ai-snp2.7:16.2_0": "so beautiful and famous,",
    "ai-snp2.7:16.3_0": "Someone with good qualities,",
    "ai-snp2.7:16.4_0": "like the hair and beards,",
    "ai-snp2.7:16.5_0": "However long as they live together",
    "ai-snp2.7:16.6_0": "and happiness as its benefit.",
    "ai-snp2.7:17.1_0": "their darts drawn out there,",
    "ai-snp2.7:17.2_0": "and Virūpakkha,",
    "ai-snp2.7:17.3_0": "Though the King of Death,",
    "ai-snp2.7:17.4_0": "they’re not stuck in the scope of logic.",
    "ai-snp2.7:18.1_0": "with chariots,",
    "ai-snp2.7:18.2_0": "Well done by you, mind?",
    "ai-snp2.7:18.3_0": "Whose home is",
    "ai-snp2.7:18.4_0": "dishaposed his share.",
    "ai-snp2.7:19.1_0": "Like the cows,",
    "ai-snp2.7:19.2_0": "dragged down this life span",
    "ai-snp2.7:19.3_0": "extremely wealthy family,",
    "ai-snp2.7:19.4_0": "who are covetous.",
    "ai-snp2.7:20.1_0": "Those carcasting them there,",
    "ai-snp2.7:20.2_0": "and went up to the aughing.",
    "ai-snp2.7:20.3_0": "He was a majestic king,",
    "ai-snp2.7:20.4_0": "a lot of string",
    "ai-snp2.7:20.5_0": "little wealth is full of fame.",
    "ai-snp2.7:21.1_0": "Since the king is restrained,",
    "ai-snp2.7:21.2_0": "a brahmin of the chariot.",
    "ai-snp2.7:21.3_0": "Horse sacrifice, human sacrifice,",
    "ai-snp2.7:21.4_0": "the sacrifices of the ‘stick-casting’,",
    "ai-snp2.7:21.5_0": "Having rained the good,",
    "ai-snp2.7:21.6_0": "than brahmins.",
    "ai-snp2.7:22.1_0": "food and drink,",
    "ai-snp2.7:22.2_0": "boat on the mountain,",
    "ai-snp2.7:22.3_0": "with chariots,",
    "ai-snp2.7:22.4_0": "Subhā, the smith’s daughter,",
    "ai-snp2.7:23.1_0": "homeless on the home",
    "ai-snp2.7:23.2_0": "shared out,",
    "ai-snp2.7:23.3_0": "these two faces of various colors,",
    "ai-snp2.7:23.4_0": "than brahmins.",
    "ai-snp2.7:24.1_0": "And there’s plenty of wealth",
    "ai-snp2.7:24.2_0": "storming, and wished,",
    "ai-snp2.7:24.3_0": "enjoying them,",
    "ai-snp2.7:24.4_0": "this craving grows up even more;",
    "ai-snp2.7:24.5_0": "Those carcasting them there,",
    "ai-snp2.7:24.6_0": "and passed from the a little hut again.",
    "ai-snp2.7:25.1_0": "Water and earth,",
    "ai-snp2.7:25.2_0": "money, and grain;",
    "ai-snp2.7:25.3_0": "Thus human creatures,",
    "ai-snp2.7:25.4_0": "for living creatures—",
    "ai-snp2.7:25.5_0": "Your Majesty, author,",
    "ai-snp2.7:25.6_0": "little wealth is full of fame.",
    "ai-snp2.7:26.1_0": "Since the king is restrained,",
    "ai-snp2.7:26.2_0": "a brahmin of the chariot.",
    "ai-snp2.7:26.3_0": "of the company of the hundreds,",
    "ai-snp2.7:26.4_0": "that the cattle-keeper gave him this sacrifice.",
    "ai-snp2.7:27.1_0": "nor fuming the feet,",
    "ai-snp2.7:27.2_0": "They don’t stay anyone.",
    "ai-snp2.7:27.3_0": "Suppose that, caravan leader,",
    "ai-snp2.7:27.4_0": "grungles, and jackals.",
    "ai-snp2.7:27.5_0": "Taking them again, they get hold of them,",
    "ai-snp2.7:27.6_0": "and the King’s thighs me with him.",
    "ai-snp2.7:28.1_0": "Then even the gods,",
    "ai-snp2.7:28.2_0": "Indra, true to their vows,",
    "ai-snp2.7:28.3_0": "Grounds for the Dhamma,",
    "ai-snp2.7:28.4_0": "that you’ve plunged into the caravan.",
    "ai-snp2.7:29.1_0": "Three others in a village;",
    "ai-snp2.7:29.2_0": "desire for old age.",
    "ai-snp2.7:29.3_0": "and listening to the true teaching—",
    "ai-snp2.7:29.4_0": "and surrounded by their mother.",
    "ai-snp2.7:30.1_0": "This being so,",
    "ai-snp2.7:30.2_0": "That was past.",
    "ai-snp2.7:30.3_0": "goats and sheep,",
    "ai-snp2.7:30.4_0": "a bier of the qualities.",
    "ai-snp2.7:31.1_0": "That is how the teaching has",
    "ai-snp2.7:31.2_0": "and winning the ancient sensible person.",
    "ai-snp2.7:31.3_0": "Wherever he sees a mattress,",
    "ai-snp2.7:31.4_0": "as people criticize it.",
    "ai-snp2.7:32.1_0": "Thus having dispensation",
    "ai-snp2.7:32.2_0": "who are divided in the midst of the Sangha,",
    "ai-snp2.7:32.3_0": "ordinary aristocrats, brahmins,",
    "ai-snp2.7:32.4_0": "you’ll be sent back to a wife.",
    "ai-snp2.7:33.1_0": "aristocrats, brahmins, and householders",
    "ai-snp2.7:33.2_0": "and others with kinsmen—",
    "ai-snp2.7:33.3_0": "and having wiped out transmigration—",
    "ai-snp2.7:33.4_0": "under the sway of sensual pleasures.”",
    "ai-snp2.7:34.1_0": "When he said this, those well-to-do brahmins said to him,",
    "ai-snp2.7:34.2_0": "“Excellent, sir! Excellent! ...",
    "ai-snp2.7:34.3_0": "Please accept us as lay followers who have gone for refuge for life.”",
    "ai-snp2.7:34.4_0": "Seventh of the brahmins."
}